description:
TPUSA Live and Breakaway Host Jon Root joins Jack Posobiec on Human Events Daily where they discuss the demise of San Francisco, the woke takeover of American sports and Jon’s journey to “the couch”.

Here is your daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
